        "Heading_color": "#f8f2e6",
        "title": "OUR FAMILY LEGACY",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>A Chenin Blanc and a Cape Fusion red wine blend soon followed, and when the time came to choose a name for his wine-making enterprise, Alvi decided to name his wines for the low-water bridge built by his grandfather back in 1930.</p><p>Widely known for his perfectionism, dedication, and passion for his craft, Alvi has turned both the farm and the family legacy for creating exceptional wine, into a vision that has surpassed all expectations.</p><p><strong>And so, Alvi’s Drift Winery was born.</strong></p>",
